{"tid":1086875,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【天命最高】《尋秦記》電影版4月正式開拍   原班人馬獨欠他？","createTime":"2019-04-01T04:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T08:18:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d91993c94797fdaef4d39f3677d3e247bd1e7dcf","tid":1086875,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"等了又等的《尋秦記》電影版，日前終於在《影視博覽2019》上宣佈4月正式開拍。電影將會由電視版的原班人馬上陣，男主角古天樂就笑指今次演員陣容是「難儲過閃咭！」其實2001年首播的《尋秦記》是改編自黃易的同名小說，可以算是穿越劇的始祖，新鮮劇情和有趣對白，令此劇被大家封為「神劇」，而劇中的角色更加個個令人印象難忘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/entertainment/a-step-into-the-past-movie-new/3119151-1-chi-HK/_1_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fentertainment%2Fa-step-into-the-past-movie-new%2F3119151-1-chi-HK%2F_1_img_750_h.jpg&h=bd3e6167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實2001年首播的《尋秦記》是改編自黃易的同名小說，可以算是穿越劇的始祖，新鮮劇情和有趣對白，令此劇被大家封為「神劇」，而劇中的角色更加個個令人印象難忘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/entertainment/a-step-into-the-past-movie-new/1-img-750-h/3119499-1-chi-HK/1-img-750-h_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fentertainment%2Fa-step-into-the-past-movie-new%2F1-img-750-h%2F3119499-1-chi-HK%2F1-img-750-h_img_750_h.jpg&h=e406eb87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《尋秦記》被稱為TVB神劇之一，對於古天樂能召集大部份原班人馬拍攝電影版，Fans大感期待。故事中哪個角色是令你最難忘，最希望他/她能夠重現大銀幕呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/entertainment/a-step-into-the-past-movie-new/poster-img-750-h/3119508-1-chi-HK/Poster-img-750-h_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fentertainment%2Fa-step-into-the-past-movie-new%2Fposter-img-75